node.text: [#sponsored] We have fallen in love with wine over the years. From being born and raised in Oregon Pinot Noir country to having the opportunity to travel and experience new regions… We have loved how connected it makes us feel to different types of soil, farming, weather, people, and culture. We partnered with @undergroundcellar to share a great way to find new wines that you wouldn’t usually find at a grocery store. Who know’s… Maybe it will inspire some new travel plans! Use code PNW50 to receive $50 off your first order at www.undergroundcellar.com (link in bio too!) and start expanding your wine knowledge today. #undergroundcellar
